room_title: Escape room "DaVinci's Office" by Southern Pines Escape in Southern Pines
room_description: Leonardo Da Vinci was one the greatest minds the world has ever known. He invented, painted, sculpted and did so many things we are still trying to figure out. You and your team of Forensic Anthropologists have been granted a rare private viewing of Leonardo’s own private quarters. Time and time again Leonardo’s riddles have baffled us. Now it’s up to you. You’ve got an hour. Can you do what many before you have tried and failed?
